spec_data.Name: liblouisutdml-devel
spec_data.Description:
liblouisutdml is a braille transcription library for UTDML (Unified Tactile
Document Markup Language) documents. The liblouisutdml-devel package contains
libraries and header files for developing applications that use liblouisutdml.
